author: Unity
description:
Unity Tower, our new high-rise building model, is a sophisticated 40+ floor mixed-use tower designed from the ground up to help you test and showcase Unity’s data streaming and BIM capabilities.

This asset was built to mirror the complexity of real-world AEC projects and is the perfect testbed for large-scale data handling.

What’s inside the Unity Tower:
- Massive scale: 80+ million triangles
- Real-world federation: Includes separate, federated models for architectural, structural, MEP, facade, and interior disciplines
- Rich detail: Features complex and detailed MEP systems, furnished interiors, facade details, and a fully realized building structure
- Mixed-use design: Office spaces, hotel facilities, retail, and Unity rooftop bar
- Industry-standard: Built in Autodesk Revit and using BIM standards for metadata and naming conventions

Learn more about the Unity Tower: https://on.unity.com/UnityTower
title: Unity Tower - 3D Data Streaming
